@startuml Manage Appointments Sequence Diagram

title Manage Appointments Flow

actor User
participant "Web App" as App
participant "Appointment Service" as Appt

User -> App: Open appointments page
App -> Appt: Fetch user appointments
Appt --> App: Return appointments
App --> User: Display appointments

User -> App: Create appointment
App -> Appt: Create new appointment
Appt --> App: Appointment created
App --> User: Creation confirmation

User -> App: Update appointment
App -> Appt: Update appointment details
Appt --> App: Appointment updated
App --> User: Update confirmation

User -> App: Delete appointment
App -> Appt: Delete appointment request
Appt --> App: Appointment deleted
App --> User: Deletion confirmation

@enduml